39
00:02:30,620 --> 00:02:32,160
Do you need to see a doctor? I'll take you there.

40
00:02:32,160 --> 00:02:34,580
Don't worry about me.

41
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:39,780
You─ I...

42
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:53,920
Now, you are experiencing feelings of anger and annoyance.

43
00:02:53,920 --> 00:02:56,400
Before we start chatting,

44
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:59,660
I want you to stay awake and focused.

45
00:02:59,660 --> 00:03:02,880
Control the rhythm of your breathing.

46
00:03:02,880 --> 00:03:05,080
Inhale deeply.

47
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:06,940
Exhale slowly.

48
00:03:06,940 --> 00:03:09,920
Give it a try. Inhale.

49
00:03:09,920 --> 00:03:12,420
Exhale.

50
00:03:13,160 --> 00:03:15,620
Inhale.

51
00:03:15,620 --> 00:03:17,840
Exhale.

52
00:03:19,460 --> 00:03:21,060
Doctor.

53
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:26,760
I don't think I can concentrate right now.

54
00:03:26,760 --> 00:03:29,360
I want you to check

55
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:33,340
and see if I'm getting worse.

56
00:03:33,340 --> 00:03:37,340
Occasionally, I don't see anything dirty,

57
00:03:37,340 --> 00:03:42,600
but I am nervous and my heart races.

58
00:03:42,600 --> 00:03:47,680
Occasionally, when I see it or think of it─

59
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:50,160
My heart races, Doctor. And I don't know why.

60
00:03:50,160 --> 00:03:53,160
- I tried my best to─
- Hold on, hold on, Khun Sira. Calm down.

61
00:03:53,160 --> 00:03:57,880
You said sometimes you didn't see anything dirty,

62
00:03:57,880 --> 00:04:00,660
but you also got nervous. Right?

63
00:04:00,660 --> 00:04:02,120
So what did you see?

64
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:05,120
I saw...

65
00:04:10,900 --> 00:04:12,380
Ask something else.

66
00:04:12,380 --> 00:04:17,400
You said when you saw it, your heart was racing.

67
00:04:17,400 --> 00:04:19,820
What did you see?

68
00:04:25,900 --> 00:04:28,660
Change the question.

69
00:04:28,660 --> 00:04:32,060
You said, "think of it". What did you think of?

70
00:04:32,060 --> 00:04:34,840
I thought of...

71
00:04:36,280 --> 00:04:39,480
I thought of...

72
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:43,220
You thought of me. Why don't you let the doctor know?

73
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:48,400
Doctor, ask something else.

74
00:04:48,400 --> 00:04:51,780
Oh, Khun Sira. I don't know what to ask you.

75
00:04:51,780 --> 00:04:54,880
Are you not answering my question because you deliberately don't want to answer

76
00:04:54,880 --> 00:04:58,160
or are you pretending not to know?

77
00:04:58,160 --> 00:05:02,740
If you don't answer my question, I can't treat your condition.

78
00:05:02,740 --> 00:05:04,700
You have to be honest with me.

79
00:05:04,700 --> 00:05:06,660
Kheetika.

80
00:05:06,660 --> 00:05:11,380
Kheetika. She's the one who makes my heart race.

81
00:05:11,380 --> 00:05:15,980
I don't understand why I have symptoms because of Kheetika.

82
00:05:15,980 --> 00:05:17,660
If you ask me,

83
00:05:17,660 --> 00:05:22,260
your symptoms have nothing to do with your condition.

84
00:05:22,260 --> 00:05:24,605
Then, what does it have to do with, Doctor?

85
00:05:30,312 --> 00:05:32,680
Love. The feeling of love.

86
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:34,980
- Love?
- Love. Right.

87
00:05:34,980 --> 00:05:39,340
Your symptom is called falling in love.

88
00:05:40,520 --> 00:05:41,920
Me?

89
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:43,618
Yes.

90
00:05:43,618 --> 00:05:45,592
- Fall in love?
- Yes!

91
00:05:45,592 --> 00:05:47,020
With whom?

92
00:05:47,020 --> 00:05:49,180
Kheetika.

93
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:52,200
Kheetika?

94
00:05:52,200 --> 00:05:54,300
It's not possible, Doctor.

95
00:05:54,300 --> 00:05:58,200
I could never fall in love with that sloppy woman.

96
00:05:58,200 --> 00:06:00,860
I think you're wrong.

97
00:06:00,860 --> 00:06:02,360
No.

98
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:06,700
If you think I'm wrong, focus and think.

99
00:06:06,700 --> 00:06:11,460
Ask yourself if you're thinking what I'm thinking.

100
00:06:14,420 --> 00:06:17,220
Didn't you say you don't like liars?

101
00:06:17,220 --> 00:06:22,980
Then, why don't you be honest with yourself?

102
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:28,400
What's wrong?

103
00:06:32,440 --> 00:06:38,160
Say it out. Say it out.

104
00:06:38,160 --> 00:06:39,820
What?

105
00:06:48,700 --> 00:06:50,300
Doctor.

106
00:06:50,300 --> 00:06:55,920
I... I'd better go back. It's late.

107
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:59,520
That's all? You would rather not continue?

108
00:06:59,520 --> 00:07:01,480
Where are you going, Khun Sira?

109
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:05,320
I can't help you with love.

110
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:21,040
Khun Kheetika?

111
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:27,200
Sorry. If there's nothing else, I'll go out.

112
00:07:30,200 --> 00:07:32,380
I brought you breakfast.

113
00:07:32,380 --> 00:07:34,060
I secretly asked Mahakul.

114
00:07:34,060 --> 00:07:37,960
He said you don't like heavy food, soups, and boiled food.

115
00:07:37,960 --> 00:07:39,760
Because they would waste your time.

116
00:07:39,760 --> 00:07:42,340
So the foods that suit you

117
00:07:42,340 --> 00:07:47,420
are stir-fried vermicelli, stewed egg with herbs, and braised eggs.

118
00:07:47,420 --> 00:07:49,240
Don't forget to eat some fruit.

119
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:52,880
I prepared some cherries and blueberries for you. They are good for your eyes.

120
00:07:52,880 --> 00:07:55,880
You use your eyes a lot at work.

121
00:07:55,880 --> 00:07:58,600
Then there's warm peppermint tea.

122
00:07:58,600 --> 00:08:01,880
You shouldn't drink too much coffee. You should have some tea.

123
00:08:01,880 --> 00:08:06,160
Don't worry. Everything is clean and hygienic.

124
00:08:06,160 --> 00:08:10,360
I watched every step in the kitchen.

125
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:12,420
Actually, I wanted to do it myself.

126
00:08:12,420 --> 00:08:16,520
But I can only make instant noodles, boiled eggs, fried eggs, and omelets.

127
00:08:20,900 --> 00:08:22,980
Could it be that Khun Sira really likes Khun Kheetika,

128
00:08:22,980 --> 00:08:25,680
and they are flirting with each other?

129
00:08:28,260 --> 00:08:30,840
Maha, use your head.

130
00:08:30,840 --> 00:08:34,300
Khun Kheetika prepared a lunchbox for Khun Sira with love.

131
00:08:34,300 --> 00:08:37,380
If it's not love, what else could it be?

132
00:08:37,380 --> 00:08:39,980
Wow, how can't he like it?

133
00:08:39,980 --> 00:08:42,440
Khun Kheetika is beautiful and cute.

134
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:43,920
I think so, too.

135
00:08:43,920 --> 00:08:47,720
Khun Sira doesn't like people who lie, but she's a liar.

136
00:08:47,720 --> 00:08:51,900
Khun Sira loves cleanliness, but Khun Kheetika doesn't love cleanliness at all.

137
00:08:51,900 --> 00:08:55,580
Khun Sira doesn't like to drink, but Khun Kheetika is an alcoholic.

138
00:08:55,580 --> 00:08:58,580
Based on these three points, there's no way they're dating.

139
00:08:58,580 --> 00:09:00,440
Why are you bullying others?

140
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:02,060
- Don't bully others.
- I'm not!

141
00:09:02,060 --> 00:09:05,240
- As a man, you shouldn't gossip about women.
- The facts are on the table.

142
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:06,880
I'm telling the truth.

143
00:09:06,880 --> 00:09:10,180
Since we all have doubts,

144
00:09:10,180 --> 00:09:11,960
we have only one way to find out the truth,

145
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:15,900
which is to ask Khun Sira directly if he likes Khun Kheetika.

146
00:09:15,900 --> 00:09:18,500
- Yes.
- Good idea, Friend.

147
00:09:18,500 --> 00:09:21,840
But who's going to ask?

148
00:09:21,840 --> 00:09:24,800
One, two, three.

149
00:09:28,100 --> 00:09:31,040
- Don't look at me. I won't ask.
- Why?

150
00:09:31,040 --> 00:09:32,580
If you want to know, ask Khun Sira yourself.

151
00:09:32,580 --> 00:09:34,940
- Don't look at me.
- Are you sure, Maha?

152
00:09:34,940 --> 00:09:36,820
Maha.

153
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:41,160
Is Khun Sira here?

154
00:09:41,160 --> 00:09:43,020
Yes.

155
00:09:45,260 --> 00:09:47,780
- She smiled, right?
- She smiled.

156
00:09:48,780 --> 00:09:52,040
Enough. Stop gossiping.

157
00:09:57,160 --> 00:09:59,220
Khun Sira.

158
00:10:02,580 --> 00:10:05,040
When will you learn how to knock?

159
00:10:06,320 --> 00:10:08,220
Sorry.

160
00:10:08,220 --> 00:10:12,638
I just want to know if you liked your meal.

161
00:10:19,720 --> 00:10:22,920
What do you want? Just tell me.

162
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:28,160
Khun Sira, please help me.

163
00:10:28,160 --> 00:10:32,000
Think of it as for the good of the company.

164
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:38,000
No. It's not my job to convince Thatha. Try to find another way.

165
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:41,120
If I could figure it out, would I come to you for help?

166
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:43,260
This is the best way.

167
00:10:43,260 --> 00:10:46,500
No, I won't help you.

168
00:10:50,150 --> 00:10:52,300
Khun Sira, if we succeed,

169
00:10:52,300 --> 00:10:56,300
we can redeem the New Look website's reputation.

170
00:10:57,200 --> 00:11:00,160
I know it's not your work.

171
00:11:00,160 --> 00:11:04,800
Think of it as if you were pitying your employee.

172
00:11:07,460 --> 00:11:12,080
So what? If I help you, when other employees come to me

173
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:14,560
with work that they can't do, should I help them?

174
00:11:14,560 --> 00:11:17,780
That's not what I meant.

175
00:11:17,780 --> 00:11:19,520
It depends on the actual situation.

176
00:11:19,520 --> 00:11:21,680
In that case, it's not suitable for me to help you.

177
00:11:21,680 --> 00:11:25,020
Khun Sira, I know I'm asking too much.

178
00:11:25,020 --> 00:11:28,320
But this job is essential to me.

179
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:32,160
I want to take responsibility for my mistakes.

180
00:11:32,160 --> 00:11:34,120
And I don't want you to feel bad.

181
00:11:34,120 --> 00:11:37,340
You gave me the chance to work here, but I let you down.

182
00:11:44,740 --> 00:11:47,020
Kheetika.

183
00:11:47,020 --> 00:11:51,100
Can you tell me where we're going to meet Khun Thatha?

184
00:11:51,100 --> 00:11:55,720
We've come a long way.

185
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:58,720
It's far away, outside of Bangkok.

186
00:11:58,720 --> 00:12:00,520
Outside of Bangkok?

187
00:12:08,790 --> 00:12:12,020
- What?
- Put your phone down, Maha.

188
00:12:12,020 --> 00:12:14,972
Khun Sira won't need you today.

189
00:12:14,972 --> 00:12:16,740
I'm Khun Sira's secretary.

190
00:12:16,740 --> 00:12:19,780
I'm the closest to him, and I know him the best.

191
00:12:19,780 --> 00:12:21,680
Why wouldn't he call me?

192
00:12:21,680 --> 00:12:24,540
Because Khun Sira already has someone who understands him.

193
00:12:24,540 --> 00:12:29,160
Why would he care about you? Got it?

194
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:37,140
All right, don't be a secretary, be a black sheep.

195
00:12:37,140 --> 00:12:39,400
Are you saying that I'm bad?

196
00:12:39,400 --> 00:12:41,100
I'm not.

197
00:12:41,100 --> 00:12:45,680
Khun Rossarin told me that black sheep means happy.

198
00:12:49,740 --> 00:12:53,978
Good. Go down some steps. Good.

199
00:12:53,978 --> 00:12:57,420
- Beautiful.
- Good.

200
00:12:57,420 --> 00:12:59,040
Good.

201
00:12:59,040 --> 00:13:02,160
Edit here.

202
00:13:02,160 --> 00:13:04,300
Hello, P'Hoymen.

203
00:13:04,300 --> 00:13:06,320
Hello, Kheetika.

204
00:13:06,320 --> 00:13:11,520
This is Khun Sira, the vice chairman of GU.

205
00:13:13,120 --> 00:13:15,220
Hello, Khun Sira.

206
00:13:15,220 --> 00:13:17,480
Hello, Khun Hoymen.

207
00:13:17,480 --> 00:13:20,180
Thatha is up there taking pictures.

208
00:13:25,220 --> 00:13:27,498
- P'Hoy.
- Hoymen.

209
00:13:27,498 --> 00:13:31,480
Whatever. Did you ask that woman to come and see me today?

210
00:13:32,100 --> 00:13:34,140
Hey, don't start yelling. Okay?

211
00:13:34,140 --> 00:13:36,740
Khun Kheetika is really sincere.

212
00:13:36,740 --> 00:13:39,080
She said there was a misunderstanding last time.

213
00:13:39,080 --> 00:13:44,160
No. I told her I would never be a backup.

214
00:13:44,160 --> 00:13:47,980
Because I'm a top model in Thailand.

215
00:13:47,980 --> 00:13:51,780
I know you're a top model. But think about it.

216
00:13:51,780 --> 00:13:58,140
GU Center is a top international mall.

217
00:13:58,140 --> 00:14:04,211
If you become a spokesperson for GU, your career will go further.

218
00:14:04,211 --> 00:14:07,420
Your worth will increase, and you will receive a lot

219
00:14:07,420 --> 00:14:10,480
of endorsements and other jobs.

220
00:14:10,480 --> 00:14:16,020
You'll be up, up, up. Then you'll be famous, famous, famous. Then you'll finally be rich, rich, rich.

221
00:14:17,170 --> 00:14:22,346
If I want to take this job, I can just talk to Sasa and be done.

222
00:14:22,346 --> 00:14:26,981
Khun Sasa of yours doesn't want you to be their spokesperson.

223
00:14:26,981 --> 00:14:31,619
If he really wanted you, he wouldn't have had Kheetika contact us.

224
00:14:32,930 --> 00:14:36,130
Honey, let me be honest with you.

225
00:14:36,130 --> 00:14:39,370
Khun Sasa isn't serious about you.

226
00:14:39,370 --> 00:14:43,570
He's just playing with you like he did last time.

227
00:14:43,570 --> 00:14:48,050
If you want to find someone you can rely on for the rest of your life,

228
00:14:48,050 --> 00:14:51,290
you should find a backup.

229
00:14:54,790 --> 00:14:59,230
What does that mean?

230
00:14:59,230 --> 00:15:04,190
Kheetika won't come here alone.

231
00:15:04,190 --> 00:15:05,850
Khun Sira will be with her.

232
00:15:05,850 --> 00:15:11,370
He's the vice chairman of GU.

233
00:15:13,445 --> 00:15:17,846
If you want to find someone to rely on,

234
00:15:17,846 --> 00:15:21,430
he's the best choice.

235
00:15:32,869 --> 00:15:36,533
Hello, may I help you?

236
00:15:36,533 --> 00:15:40,686
I want to see... see...

237
00:15:42,003 --> 00:15:44,163
I want to─

238
00:15:45,950 --> 00:15:47,850
Hom?

239
00:15:55,523 --> 00:15:59,463
Hello, Mahakul. Where did my brother go?

240
00:15:59,463 --> 00:16:02,436
I called him, but he didn't answer.

241
00:16:03,760 --> 00:16:06,783
Hello, Director of New Look.

242
00:16:07,890 --> 00:16:12,430
I heard that a designer named Kheetika made the New Look website famous.

243
00:16:12,430 --> 00:16:16,230
She made customers make a scene in the mall.

244
00:16:21,470 --> 00:16:23,870
I wanted to call and ask where my brother was.

245
00:16:23,870 --> 00:16:27,230
But now I want to talk to you

246
