- This way.

505
00:35:39,550 --> 00:35:40,370
Something is wrong.

506
00:35:40,370 --> 00:35:42,130
Not now. Let's go up there first.

507
00:35:42,130 --> 00:35:44,050
Wait.

508
00:35:44,050 --> 00:35:46,990
Otherwise, we won't be able to make it up to greet Khun Sira in line.

509
00:35:46,990 --> 00:35:49,510
You don't have to line up to greet Khun Sira.

510
00:35:49,510 --> 00:35:50,450
Why?

511
00:35:50,450 --> 00:35:52,150
Because Khun Sira is not coming today.

512
00:35:52,150 --> 00:35:54,150
What? Khun Sira isn't coming?

513
00:35:54,150 --> 00:35:55,770
P'Maha!

514
00:35:55,770 --> 00:35:57,070
What happened?

515
00:35:57,070 --> 00:35:59,370
Why didn't Khun Sira come to work?

516
00:35:59,370 --> 00:36:01,810
Tell us everything you know.

517
00:36:01,810 --> 00:36:02,790
Quickly.

518
00:36:02,790 --> 00:36:04,190
I don't know anything.

519
00:36:04,190 --> 00:36:06,650
Khun Sira called and said he was tired.

520
00:36:06,650 --> 00:36:07,930
He'll come to work in the afternoon.

521
00:36:07,930 --> 00:36:08,970
Is Khun Sira sick?

522
00:36:08,970 --> 00:36:11,150
No. It's not possible.

523
00:36:11,150 --> 00:36:12,730
He loves cleanliness.

524
00:36:12,730 --> 00:36:15,390
Bacteria would have been wiped out a hundred meters away.

525
00:36:15,390 --> 00:36:17,740
True, ever since I came here to work,

526
00:36:17,740 --> 00:36:21,210
I've never heard Khun Sira cough at all.

527
00:36:21,210 --> 00:36:22,350
So, what's the deal?

528
00:36:22,350 --> 00:36:24,050
Is there something you're not telling us?

529
00:36:24,050 --> 00:36:26,850
I also want to know like you all.

530
00:36:26,850 --> 00:36:28,090
You have so many questions.

531
00:36:28,090 --> 00:36:31,030
If P'Maha doesn't know, who would?

532
00:36:31,030 --> 00:36:34,570
- Are you sure?
- Khun Kheetika.

533
00:36:34,570 --> 00:36:38,490
Khun Kheetika and Khun Sira left Bangkok yesterday.

534
00:36:38,490 --> 00:36:43,290
So, Khun Kheetika must know what happened to Khun Sira.

535
00:36:43,290 --> 00:36:47,210
Khun Kheetika and Khun Sira left Bangkok.

536
00:36:47,210 --> 00:36:48,550
Then─

537
00:36:49,410 --> 00:36:52,050
Hey, Kirin, you're imagining things, aren't you?

538
00:36:52,050 --> 00:36:53,290
No, I'm not.

539
00:36:53,290 --> 00:36:57,030
I just wanted to applaud Khun Pa's intelligence. She's smart.

540
00:36:57,030 --> 00:37:01,230
They left Bangkok together.

541
00:37:02,790 --> 00:37:05,170
Stop applauding! Nothing happened!

542
00:37:05,170 --> 00:37:07,610
There's no way that Khun Sira and Khun Kheetika did that.

543
00:37:07,610 --> 00:37:09,310
No!

544
00:37:09,310 --> 00:37:12,410
Go. Let's go,

545
00:37:12,410 --> 00:37:15,750
What happened? I feel dizzy.

546
00:37:24,450 --> 00:37:26,290
Are you awake?

547
00:37:26,290 --> 00:37:27,250
Khun Sira.

548
00:37:27,250 --> 00:37:29,070
What is it?

549
00:37:32,970 --> 00:37:34,910
I'm coming in.

550
00:37:48,510 --> 00:37:51,790
Can you sit up? Wait.

551
00:37:52,990 --> 00:37:54,670
Your face is still pale.

552
00:37:54,670 --> 00:37:57,490
Are you still having diarrhea?

553
00:37:57,490 --> 00:37:59,670
Do you want to go to the hospital? I'll take you there.

554
00:37:59,670 --> 00:38:01,537
I'm not going to the hospital.

555
00:38:01,537 --> 00:38:03,023
I'll be fine after taking the medicine and sleeping for a while.

556
00:38:03,023 --> 00:38:05,810
What's wrong with the hospital?

557
00:38:05,810 --> 00:38:08,630
I wanted to take you there yesterday, but you kept complaining.

558
00:38:09,570 --> 00:38:12,730
If I can't hold on, I'll call Dr. Zhao.

559
00:38:14,030 --> 00:38:16,050
Okay. Your decision.

560
00:38:16,050 --> 00:38:18,570
Be careful what you eat next time.

561
00:38:18,570 --> 00:38:22,090
So you won't get diarrhea again.

562
00:38:22,090 --> 00:38:25,330
It's all your fault. You bought the food.

563
00:38:25,330 --> 00:38:27,050
Hey, don't blame me.

564
00:38:27,050 --> 00:38:30,330
I also ate it. But I don't have diarrhea.

565
00:38:32,790 --> 00:38:36,870
Be good. Eat before you take your medicine.

566
00:38:42,270 --> 00:38:44,390
Let's eat.

567
00:38:49,070 --> 00:38:50,670
Open your mouth.

568
00:38:56,070 --> 00:38:57,810
I can eat it myself.

569
00:38:58,623 --> 00:38:59,696
Okay.

570
00:38:59,696 --> 00:39:01,196
Ah, it's so hot.

571
00:39:05,350 --> 00:39:07,550
You're taking care of me.

572
00:39:08,470 --> 00:39:11,230
Aren't you mad at me for Khun Thatha?

573
00:39:12,030 --> 00:39:13,530
I'm angry.

574
00:39:14,530 --> 00:39:18,610
But that's work. It has nothing to do with you being sick.

575
00:39:18,610 --> 00:39:21,190
Don't ask so much. Eat your meal.

576
00:39:22,050 --> 00:39:25,010
You're mean. I'm so scared.

577
00:39:34,370 --> 00:39:36,390
Hello, Khun Hoymen.

578
00:39:40,192 --> 00:39:41,910
Thank you.

579
00:39:44,610 --> 00:39:47,010
About what happened yesterday,

580
00:39:47,010 --> 00:39:51,310
I want to sincerely apologize to you, Khun Kheetika.

581
00:39:51,310 --> 00:39:54,430
Nong Thatha is not that kind of person.

582
00:39:54,430 --> 00:39:57,570
She was tired from work yesterday.

583
00:39:57,570 --> 00:40:02,230
So she was a little upset. That's why it happened.

584
00:40:02,230 --> 00:40:06,230
Khun Kheetika, I hope you don't get mad at Nong Thatha.

585
00:40:06,230 --> 00:40:07,550
It's all right.

586
00:40:07,550 --> 00:40:10,811
It's water under the bridge. And I'm not taking it personally.

587
00:40:10,811 --> 00:40:14,211
Actually, Nong Thatha wanted to come today.

588
00:40:14,211 --> 00:40:16,710
But she's sick.

589
00:40:16,710 --> 00:40:22,109
She was so distressed that she went to the hospital.

590
00:40:22,109 --> 00:40:23,970
She went to the hospital?

591
00:40:23,970 --> 00:40:26,510
Which hospital? I'll visit her later.

592
00:40:30,470 --> 00:40:32,850
Thank you. But don't bother.

593
00:40:32,850 --> 00:40:34,910
Thatha doesn't want too many people to know.

594
00:40:34,910 --> 00:40:36,930
She's worried about it being in the news.

595
00:40:36,930 --> 00:40:39,450
When Thatha feels better,

596
00:40:39,450 --> 00:40:44,490
I'll bring her to apologize to you again.

597
00:40:44,490 --> 00:40:48,330
Why did Khun Thatha suddenly change her mind and want to become our spokesperson?

598
00:40:48,330 --> 00:40:53,470
Nong Thatha was very upset that she made you think

599
00:40:53,470 --> 00:40:56,250
she was a person who only looked beautiful on the outside.

600
00:40:56,250 --> 00:41:01,170
In fact, she's beautiful inside and outside.

601
00:41:01,170 --> 00:41:05,470
She's the perfect spokesperson for New Look.

602
00:41:05,470 --> 00:41:07,698
I hope we can work together well.

603
00:41:07,698 --> 00:41:08,969
Definitely.

604
00:41:08,969 --> 00:41:14,150
Who wouldn't want to work with such a top model?

605
00:41:15,550 --> 00:41:21,350
She's really... really perfect in every way.

606
00:41:21,350 --> 00:41:24,670
So when do we sign the contract?

607
00:41:32,445 --> 00:41:36,012
I want to do it as soon as possible. Does it work for you? How about tomorrow?

608
00:41:36,012 --> 00:41:38,570
Great! What are we waiting for?

609
00:41:38,570 --> 00:41:41,010
We can sign it at any time.

610
00:41:42,070 --> 00:41:43,510
Great.

611
00:41:43,510 --> 00:41:46,490
I feel much better now.

612
00:41:46,490 --> 00:41:51,550
One, two. One, two, three. One, two. One, two, one.

613
00:41:52,470 --> 00:41:53,690
Khun Kheetika.

614
00:41:53,690 --> 00:41:57,850
No wonder you're Khun Sira's special assistant.

615
00:41:57,850 --> 00:42:00,960
You know what? When Thatha rejected us the first time,

616
00:42:00,960 --> 00:42:05,350
we were so upset.

617
00:42:05,350 --> 00:42:08,150
When you say that we have succeeded,

618
00:42:08,150 --> 00:42:14,000
our sadness has turned into happiness.

619
00:42:15,290 --> 00:42:17,265
I don't want to take all the credit.

620
00:42:17,265 --> 00:42:18,950
Khun Sira deserves some credit.

621
00:42:18,950 --> 00:42:21,430
If Khun Sira hadn't helped negotiate,

622
00:42:21,430 --> 00:42:24,150
things wouldn't have gone so well.

623
00:42:26,017 --> 00:42:28,537
Really?

624
00:42:28,537 --> 00:42:35,110
I've never seen Khun Sira so eager to help his staff.

625
00:42:35,110 --> 00:42:38,070
Yes. He treats you carefully and specially,

626
00:42:38,070 --> 00:42:40,350
unlike other employees.

627
00:42:40,350 --> 00:42:42,610
It's like...

628
00:42:42,610 --> 00:42:44,310
Like what?

629
00:42:47,510 --> 00:42:51,090
Like the boss and his employee.

630
00:42:51,090 --> 00:42:56,656
Since there's good news, let's go celebrate.

631
00:42:58,150 --> 00:43:02,510
Which restaurant should we go to? What should we eat?

632
00:43:02,510 --> 00:43:04,210
What are you celebrating?

633
00:43:06,330 --> 00:43:09,110
We're celebrating the fact that Khun Thatha will be our spokesperson.

634
00:43:09,110 --> 00:43:11,030
Did she really agree?

635
00:43:12,950 --> 00:43:14,370
I feel sorry for you.

636
00:43:14,370 --> 00:43:17,450
Your plan to stop me didn't work out.

637
00:43:20,310 --> 00:43:21,570
Good for you.

638
00:43:21,570 --> 00:43:23,810
You made Thatha change her mind.

639
00:43:25,030 --> 00:43:27,790
Even if Thatha agrees to be our spokesperson,

640
00:43:28,650 --> 00:43:31,070
it doesn't mean that everything will work out.

641
00:43:32,330 --> 00:43:35,970
What? What are you up to?

642
00:43:39,050 --> 00:43:41,230
It's not fun to say it now.

643
00:43:51,450 --> 00:43:54,050
Excuse me, Khun Sira.

644
00:44:01,090 --> 00:44:03,050
Khun Sira?

645
00:44:03,050 --> 00:44:05,630
Khun Sira, are you still having diarrhea?

646
00:44:10,030 --> 00:44:11,370
I told you not to come.

647
00:44:11,370 --> 00:44:13,470
Look at you. Let's go to the hospital.

648
00:44:13,470 --> 00:44:15,830
It's all right.

649
00:44:15,830 --> 00:44:17,910
I'll ask Maha to do it.

650
00:44:23,770 --> 00:44:25,410
Maha.

651
00:44:25,410 --> 00:44:27,270
Take Khun Sira to the hospital. Hurry.

652
00:44:27,270 --> 00:44:30,250
Khun Kheetika, don't worry. I'll take care of Khun Sira.

653
00:44:30,250 --> 00:44:32,050
Khun Sira, are you all right?

654
00:44:32,050 --> 00:44:33,770
Come on, Khun Sira.

655
00:44:33,770 --> 00:44:35,890
Be careful.

656
00:44:35,890 --> 00:44:38,370
Khun Sira, I've contacted Dr. Zhao.

657
00:44:38,370 --> 00:44:41,530
Dr. Zhao will go to your home to see you.

658
00:44:41,530 --> 00:44:43,230
Why does he have to go home?

659
00:44:43,230 --> 00:44:45,530
It's a waste of time. Let's go to the hospital.

660
00:44:45,530 --> 00:44:49,670
Khun Sira doesn't like to go to the hospital. Because it's full of bacteria.

661
00:44:49,670 --> 00:44:51,910
If he sees dirty things there,

662
00:44:51,910 --> 00:44:55,870
his cleanliness issue will make his condition worse.

663
00:44:55,870 --> 00:44:57,116
- Maha.
- Yes.

664
00:44:57,116 --> 00:44:59,081
- Hurry and take me home.
- Yes.

665
00:44:59,081 --> 00:45:02,553
Come on. Be careful, Khun Sira.

666
00:45:02,553 --> 00:45:04,390
Are you okay, Khun Sira?

667
00:45:25,436 --> 00:45:27,688
Doctor, he ate normal things.

668
00:45:27,688 --> 00:45:30,633
I ate the same as him, but I'm fine.

669
00:45:30,633 --> 00:45:34,398
Khun Sira is sensitive to strange things.

670
00:45:34,398 --> 00:45:39,750
When he eats something that is a little strange or unclean, it can have this kind of effect on his body.

671
00:45:39,750 --> 00:45:41,829
What can he eat?

672
00:45:41,829 --> 00:45:45,437
Can he eat fish porridge or something?

673
00:45:45,449 --> 00:45:49,394
Ordinary porridge is all right.

674
00:45:49,394 --> 00:45:53,739
Tonight, I'll leave it to you to take good care of Khun Sira.

675
00:45:53,739 --> 00:45:55,684
His condition is still weak.

676
00:45:55,684 --> 00:45:58,808
Don't let him move around too much.

677
00:45:58,808 --> 00:46:00,955
I'll leave. See you.

678
00:46:00,955 --> 00:46:03,290
- Goodbye.
- Goodbye.

679
00:46:18,685 --> 00:46:20,670
Would you like some water?

680
00:46:23,990 --> 00:46:26,370
Why are you dressed like this?

681
00:46:28,530 --> 00:46:30,930
- Whose bed is that?
- It's mine.

682
00:46:30,930 --> 00:46:32,430
I'm sleeping here tonight.

683
00:46:32,430 --> 00:46:35,070
No need. I can take care of myself.

684
00:46:35,070 --> 00:46:36,470
- You can sleep in your room.
- No.

685
00:46:36,470 --> 00:46:40,550
I'll sleep here. Don't try to drive me away.

686
00:46:40,550 --> 00:46:43,170
If you understand, go to sleep.

687
00:47:06,510 --> 00:47:08,150
Hey.

688
00:47:09,263 --> 00:47:11,017
Can you move over? I want to go to the bathroom.

689
00:47:11,017 --> 00:47:13,050
Wait.

690
00:47:16,910 --> 00:47:19,750
It's all right. I can walk there by myself.

691
00:47:19,750 --> 00:47:22,830
If you don't let me help you, I'll carry you there.

692
00:47:22,830 --> 00:47:24,550
Can you carry me?

693
00:47:24,550 --> 00:47:26,390
I mean it.

694
00:47:27,990 --> 00:47:30,230
Be careful.

695
00:47:30,230 --> 00:47:32,190
Slowly.

696
00:47:32,190 --> 00:47:33,670
Okay.

697
00:47:33,670 --> 00:47:35,070
Go in there.

698
00:47:35,070 --> 00:47:36,630
Wait.

699
00:47:36,630 --> 00:47:41,330
Do you want to go into the bathroom with me?

700
00:47:41,330 --> 00:47:43,870
- Yes.
- You don't have to.

701
00:47:43,890 --> 00:47:45,030
Don't worry.

702
00:47:45,030 --> 00:47:47,750
I'll close my eyes. I won't peek.

703
00:47:47,750 --> 00:47:50,150
Go out. No. Are you crazy?

704
00:47:50,150 --> 00:47:51,290
What?

705
00:47:51,290 --> 00:47:52,790
No. Go out.

706
00:47:52,790 --> 00:47:54,510
Why?

707
00:47:54,510 --> 00:47:58,710
Wait outside.

708
00:47:58,710 --> 00:48:00,710
Don't lock the door.

709
00:48:05,290 --> 00:48:07,350
- Don't lock the door.
- Okay.

710
00:48:07,350 --> 00:48:08,916
Okay.

711
00:48:58,137 --> 00:48:59,609
We can start the meeting.

712
00:48:59,609 --> 00:49:02,970
Khun Thatha asked for an assistant.

713
00:49:02,970 --> 00:49:05,010
Did you discuss it with your team?

714
00:49:05,010 --> 00:49:07,970
Who will be Thatha's design assistant?

715
00:49:07,970 --> 00:49:11,890
I've talked to the Design Department about Khun Thatha's assistant.

716
00:49:11,890 --> 00:49:14,710
When? Why don't I know?

717
00:49:14,710 --> 00:49:19,465
Do I need your permission to have a meeting with my employees, Khun Kheetika?

718
00:49:19,465 --> 00:49:22,370
You don't need my permission. But you should let me know,

719
00:49:22,370 --> 00:49:24,490
because I'm also in charge of the Design Department.

720
00:49:24,490 --> 00:49:28,990
I'll remember it. But whether I do it or not is another matter.

721
00:49:28,990 --> 00:49:34,250
The person who will be Khun Thatha's assistant is Khun Kansinee.

722
00:49:35,690 --> 00:49:38,645
Khun Sasa, thank you for giving me the chance.

723
00:49:38,645 --> 00:49:41,550
You're a good designer with no bad history.

724
00:49:41,550 --> 00:49:43,430
You deserve a good chance.

725
00:49:43,430 --> 00:49:46,010
I will do my best

726
00:49:46,010 --> 00:49:49,830
to make up for last time.

727
00:49:51,110 --> 00:49:54,070
If there's nothing else, I'll go first.

728
00:49:54,070 --> 00:49:56,270
I have an appointment with Thatha.

729
00:50:08,950 --> 00:50:12,530
Women in the 5G Era must be beautiful inside and outside.

730
00:50:12,530 --> 00:50:16,890
Visit our website, New Look, to change your life.

731
00:50:21,018 --> 00:50:22,810
Cut!

732
00:50:22,810 --> 00:50:25,770
We'll do it again later.

733
00:50:27,283 --> 00:50:29,415
What's wrong, Thatha?

734
00:50:29,415 --> 00:50:31,260
I'm sorry.

735
00:50:31,260 --> 00:50:34,070
It's dusty here.

736
00:50:34,070 --> 00:50:37,550
The fan blew dust into my nose.

737
00:50:37,550 --> 00:50:40,791
Can I take a break?

738
00:50:40,791 --> 00:50:43,690
Okay. You can take a break.

739
00:50:43,690 --> 00:50:45,030
Let's take a 10-minute break.

740
00:50:45,030 --> 00:50:46,590
Excuse us.

741
00:50:46,590 --> 00:50:50,070
Khun Thatha, is everything okay?

742
00:50:55,570 --> 00:50:58,270
Everything is okay, Khun Kheetika.

743
00:50:58,270 --> 00:51:01,670
If you need anything, just tell me.

744
00:51:01,670 --> 00:51:06,770
Could you please get me a cup of coffee?

745
00:51:07,903 --> 00:51:10,979
Babe, don't bother Khun Kheetika.

746
00:51:10,979 --> 00:51:13,550
I'll get it for you later.

747
00:51:14,550 --> 00:51:17,830
P'Hoymen, aren't you going to deal with my schedule?

748
00:51:17,830 --> 00:51:22,490
It's a waste of time for you to get me coffee.

749
00:51:22,490 --> 00:51:24,025
It's all right.

750
00:51:24,025 --> 00:51:26,130
I'll get it for you.

751
00:51:26,130 --> 00:51:27,390
Okay.

752
00:51:27,390 --> 00:51:29,830
- Thank you.
- No problem.

753
00:51:33,570 --> 00:51:37,343
Thatha, it's not good for you to order her around.

754
00:51:40,510 --> 00:51:44,110
- It's dusty.
- Just put up with it.

755
00:51:44,110 --> 00:51:46,730
Khun Thatha, here's your hot coffee.

756
00:51:46,730 --> 00:51:51,116
I forgot to tell you I wanted iced coffee.

757
00:51:51,116 --> 00:51:53,512
- Okay.
- Thank you.

758
00:51:53,512 --> 00:51:55,290
Here's your iced coffee.

759
00:51:55,290 --> 00:51:56,870
Thank you.

760
00:51:56,870 --> 00:51:58,802
Could you please get me some water?

761
00:51:58,802 --> 00:52:02,033
I want mineral water. Ordinary water makes me dizzy.

762
00:52:02,033 --> 00:52:03,638
Which brand of water do you want?

763
00:52:03,638 --> 00:52:06,371
I can't think of its name now.

764
00:52:06,371 --> 00:52:10,290
Could you buy a bottle of each brand?

765
00:52:10,290 --> 00:52:12,450
All brands?

766
00:52:31,670 --> 00:52:33,830
What?

767
00:52:34,670 --> 00:52:38,730
